<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 22:06:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“放弃责任”：法院裁定以色列政府未能促进回收竞争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/abandoned-its-responsibility-court-rules-govt-failed-to-enable-recycling-competition/0000018d-2d80-dd75-addd-ffe1af8e0000</link><description>法院对一家回收公司提交的请愿书作出的判决称，环保部未履行其法律责任，并责令其成立专门的工作组并改变其政策</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 20:42:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/abandoned-its-responsibility-court-rules-govt-failed-to-enable-recycling-competition/0000018d-2d80-dd75-addd-ffe1af8e0000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列的所有批评都是威胁时，每一位左翼教师都是叛徒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-21/ty-article/.highlight/when-all-criticism-in-israel-is-a-threat-every-leftist-teacher-is-a-traitor/0000018d-2d13-db77-ad9f-ff33b7370000</link><description>导致一名 16 岁女孩希望老师得癌症的内心仇恨并非诞生于 10 月 7 日，也不会在最后一支部队离开加沙时消散</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 19:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-21/ty-article/.highlight/when-all-criticism-in-israel-is-a-threat-every-leftist-teacher-is-a-traitor/0000018d-2d13-db77-ad9f-ff33b7370000</guid></item><item><title>两名真主党成员在黎巴嫩南部据称被以色列无人机袭击身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/two-hezbollah-members-killed-in-alleged-israeli-drone-strike-in-southern-lebanon/0000018d-2d4d-db77-ad9f-ff7f67350000</link><description>这次袭击造成一名真主党成员死亡，七人受伤，其中包括一名情况危急的妇女，据称是以色列在黎巴嫩定点清除战略转变的一部分。真主党证实其一名成员被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 19:16:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/two-hezbollah-members-killed-in-alleged-israeli-drone-strike-in-southern-lebanon/0000018d-2d4d-db77-ad9f-ff7f67350000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布备忘录解释为何对以色列发动战争；加沙人质疑时机，批评哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-releases-memo-explaining-why-it-waged-war-on-israel-gazans-question-timing/0000018d-2d3a-db77-ad9f-ff3abfd30000</link><description>该文件声称，这次致命袭击是为了阻止西岸的犹太化并结束对加沙的封锁。该文件发布的时间引发了疑问：加沙的消息人士，包括那些认同哈马斯的消息人士表示，哈马斯正在应对对加沙人付出的沉重代价的批评</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 19:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-releases-memo-explaining-why-it-waged-war-on-israel-gazans-question-timing/0000018d-2d3a-db77-ad9f-ff3abfd30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：疑似被俘的以色列士兵于 10 月 7 日被杀，其尸体被扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-israeli-soldier-thought-to-be-captured-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-2d10-dd75-addd-fff189690000</link><description>以色列军方确定，19岁的职业排球运动员谢伊·莱文森于10月7日在装甲旅服役时身亡。他现在被正式视为被恐怖组织关押的阵亡士兵</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 18:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-israeli-soldier-thought-to-be-captured-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-2d10-dd75-addd-fff189690000</guid></item><item><title>沙特外长：如果不与巴勒斯坦国建立正常关系，以色列就没有正常关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/saudi-foreign-minister-no-normal-israel-ties-without-path-to-palestinian-state/0000018d-2cdb-dd75-addd-fefbe8550000</link><description>沙特外长费萨尔·本·法尔汉·阿勒沙特亲王声称利雅得将承认以色列作为更广泛政治协议的一部分，几天后明确表示，只有通过“解决巴勒斯坦问题”才能实现地区稳定</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 16:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/saudi-foreign-minister-no-normal-israel-ties-without-path-to-palestinian-state/0000018d-2cdb-dd75-addd-fefbe8550000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官对 10 月 7 日大屠杀的说法不正确；以色列国防军：“我们将澄清事实”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/army-officer-makes-incorrect-claims-on-oct-7-massacre-idf-well-set-record-straight/0000018d-2c67-daf5-a1bf-ac77f9b50000</link><description>在接受以色列右翼新闻频道采访时，一名以色列国防军高级指挥官描述了他在 10 月 7 日与哈马斯作战时亲眼目睹的两起事件，其中包括被谋杀的婴儿和一名大屠杀幸存者被谋杀——这从未发生过，贝埃里基布兹说</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 16:18:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/army-officer-makes-incorrect-claims-on-oct-7-massacre-idf-well-set-record-straight/0000018d-2c67-daf5-a1bf-ac77f9b50000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯卫生部报告加沙死亡人数超过25,000人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/hamas-health-ministry-reports-gaza-death-toll-crosses-25-000/0000018d-2c75-db77-ad9f-ff775a870000</link><description>哈马斯控制的卫生部在一份声明中表示，自10月7日以来，以色列的袭击已造成25,105名巴勒斯坦人死亡，62,681人受伤。它没有区分平民和武装分子的死亡，但表示大多数遇难者是平民</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 15:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/hamas-health-ministry-reports-gaza-death-toll-crosses-25-000/0000018d-2c75-db77-ad9f-ff775a870000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列永远无法摧毁加沙的所有哈马斯隧道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-israel-will-never-manage-to-destroy-all-hamas-tunnels-in-gaza/0000018d-213e-dd75-addd-f3ff564f0000</link><description>加沙地下的隧道先于 1987 年哈马斯成立，并于 2007 年政变上台。现在，经过数月的努力，以色列军队可能不得不承认，摧毁绵延数英里的迷宫般的地下通道从来都不现实</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 14:37:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-israel-will-never-manage-to-destroy-all-hamas-tunnels-in-gaza/0000018d-213e-dd75-addd-f3ff564f0000</guid></item><item><title>冰球惨败后，以色列运动员是否会面临“无声抵制”？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/after-ice-hockey-fiasco-do-israeli-athletes-face-a-silent-boycott/0000018d-2c02-db77-ad9f-ff323cd40000</link><description>尽管国际冰球联合会禁止以色列球队参赛的决定被撤销，但其他运动项目面临的危险尚未过去</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 14:35:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/after-ice-hockey-fiasco-do-israeli-athletes-face-a-silent-boycott/0000018d-2c02-db77-ad9f-ff323cd40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新闻媒体错误翻译内塔尼亚胡的话，引发媒体风暴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/israel-based-news-outlet-incorrectly-translates-pms-words-leading-to-media-firestorm/0000018d-2bfa-daf5-a1bf-affa764b0000</link><description>以色列新闻频道i24将总理声明“以色列必须对约旦河以西的整个领土拥有安全控制权”错误翻译为“以色列必须控制从河流到大海”，导致被指控蓄意挑衅内塔尼亚胡</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 13:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/israel-based-news-outlet-incorrectly-translates-pms-words-leading-to-media-firestorm/0000018d-2bfa-daf5-a1bf-affa764b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长反对拒绝向哈马斯恐怖分子提供公共法律代表的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-opposes-bill-to-deny-public-legal-representation-to-hamas-terrorists/0000018d-2bdd-dd75-addd-fbfdee9a0000</link><description>根据极右翼议员 Simcha Rothman 提出的法案，10 月 7 日被捕的哈马斯恐怖分子将被剥夺公共法律代理权。以色列总检察长认为这可能会削弱针对他们的诉讼的国际合法性</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 13:21:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-opposes-bill-to-deny-public-legal-representation-to-hamas-terrorists/0000018d-2bdd-dd75-addd-fbfdee9a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列同意通过挪威向巴勒斯坦权力机构转移税收资金的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-okays-plan-to-transfer-tax-funds-to-palestinian-authority-through-norway/0000018d-2ba3-dd75-addd-fbe30cfc0000</link><description>根据临时和平协议，以色列代表巴勒斯坦人征税。 11月，以色列决定扣除巴勒斯坦权力机构用于加沙的税收资金，称这些资金最终将落入哈马斯手中，并在战争中用于对抗以色列</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 11:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-okays-plan-to-transfer-tax-funds-to-palestinian-authority-through-norway/0000018d-2ba3-dd75-addd-fbe30cfc0000</guid></item><item><title>“除了‘双重标准’和‘反犹太主义’之外，我们难道就没有一个好的反驳理由了吗？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dont-we-have-a-single-good-counterargument-except-double-standard-and-antisemitism/0000018d-1d3b-d022-ad9d-1f3f2a5d0000</link><description>纪录片《以色列主义》记录了年轻的美国犹太人对犹太国家日益失望的情况。自 10 月 7 日大屠杀以来，抵制该片的呼声不断，犹太导演被指控反犹太主义</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 10:46:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dont-we-have-a-single-good-counterargument-except-double-standard-and-antisemitism/0000018d-1d3b-d022-ad9d-1f3f2a5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人和巴勒斯坦人接受加沙“事后”计划需要的不仅仅是想象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/the-other-day-after-netanyahus-exit-wont-solve-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018d-280a-dd75-addd-faeb5ae80000</link><description>拜登政府似乎并不明白，尽管我们多么渴望生活在内塔尼亚胡不再担任领导人的以色列，但除掉他并不是他们所希望的灵丹妙药</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 10:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/the-other-day-after-netanyahus-exit-wont-solve-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018d-280a-dd75-addd-faeb5ae80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察在耶路撒冷足球赛斗殴中袭击国土报记者哈伊姆·莱文森</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-assaults-haaretz-journalist-during-soccer-match-brawl-in-jerusalem/0000018d-2b0e-dd75-addd-fbef81e10000</link><description>《国土报》专栏作家哈伊姆·莱文森在球场内遭到袭击，因为他拍到了一名穿着便衣的警察殴打俱乐部另一名球迷的照片。当莱文森拍摄这一事件时，警察掐住了莱文森的脖子，并打碎了他的眼镜</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 10:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-assaults-haaretz-journalist-during-soccer-match-brawl-in-jerusalem/0000018d-2b0e-dd75-addd-fbef81e10000</guid></item><item><title>&amp;#39;以色列？不是叫巴勒斯坦吗？”：以色列人在 WhatsApp、亚马逊甚至 Grindr 上报告反以色列闪电战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-isnt-it-called-palestine-israelis-experience-attacks-on-whatsapp-and-amazon/0000018d-1774-d695-a3dd-5775974c0000</link><description>以色列人在社交媒体上遭受大量的个人骚扰，甚至受到海外客户服务人员的敌意</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 09:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-isnt-it-called-palestine-israelis-experience-attacks-on-whatsapp-and-amazon/0000018d-1774-d695-a3dd-5775974c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了在加沙地带南部战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-combat-in-the-south-of-the-gaza-strip/0000018d-2aef-dd75-addd-faeffc690000</link><description>中士。 23 岁的尤里尔·阿维亚德·西尔伯曼 (Uriel Aviad Silberman) 少校在战前几个月完成了装甲部队的应征入伍服役。 10 月 7 日事件发生后，他被要求入伍服预备役。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 07:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-combat-in-the-south-of-the-gaza-strip/0000018d-2aef-dd75-addd-faeffc690000</guid></item><item><title>1934 年在圣经基泽尔发现的具有 5000 年历史的独特陶器终于亮相</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-01-21/ty-article/unique-5-000-year-old-pots-found-at-biblical-gezer-in-1934-are-finally-revealed/0000018d-1cbc-dd75-addd-fefdacc80000</link><description>英国考古学家艾伦·罗 (Alan Rowe) 发掘盖泽 (Gezer) 近一个世纪后，塞缪尔·沃尔夫 (Samuel Wolff) 博士发表了有关该遗址的最终报告，其中包括三艘船只的用途无法解释的情况</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 07:34:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-01-21/ty-article/unique-5-000-year-old-pots-found-at-biblical-gezer-in-1934-are-finally-revealed/0000018d-1cbc-dd75-addd-fefdacc80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属加大对内塔尼亚胡的压力，因为他拒绝哈马斯的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article-live/senior-pa-official-u-s-talk-of-two-states-is-slogan-to-pressure-netanyahu/0000018d-29e5-daf5-a1bf-adf528170000</link><description>以色列国防军：据信被俘的以色列士兵于 10 月 7 日被杀，其尸体被扣押在加沙 ■ 沙特外长：如果没有通往巴勒斯坦国的途径，以色列就没有正常关系 ■ 两名真主党成员在黎巴嫩空袭中丧生 ■ 以色列批准允许资金转移的大纲通过挪威飞往巴勒斯坦权力机构 ■ 以色列国防军公布周六在加沙南部战斗中阵亡的以色列士兵姓名</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 03:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article-live/senior-pa-official-u-s-talk-of-two-states-is-slogan-to-pressure-netanyahu/0000018d-29e5-daf5-a1bf-adf528170000</guid></item></channel></rss>